1
00:00:17,960 --> 00:00:19,520
-Where is it?
-(BEEPING)

2
00:00:19,720 --> 00:00:21,480
Oh, it just happened.
I went to the bathroom.

3
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:23,120
Thank you for the hologram leopard,
by the way.

4
00:00:23,240 --> 00:00:26,960
An unexpected pleasure.
And my bedroom was completely missing.

5
00:00:27,840 --> 00:00:29,800
(SIGHS) Just tell me where you put it.

6
00:00:31,960 --> 00:00:33,840
Hang on, I know what the problem is.

7
00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:35,600
Is this the first time
he's brought a girl home?

8
00:00:35,680 --> 00:00:37,920
(BEEPING)

9
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:40,200
Are you laughing? You are, aren't you?

10
00:00:40,280 --> 00:00:41,720
What's so funny?

11
00:00:43,960 --> 00:00:46,160
(BEEPING)

12
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:48,160
Blimey.

13
00:00:48,240 --> 00:00:50,360
That's, um... That's quite a selection.

14
00:00:50,440 --> 00:00:52,360
Dear God, that woman is made of legs.

15
00:00:52,440 --> 00:00:54,960
That's the most legs
on any living human.

16
00:00:56,960 --> 00:00:58,240
Okay.

17
00:00:58,840 --> 00:01:00,680
-Not the first, then.
-(BEEPING)

18
00:01:00,760 --> 00:01:02,240
This is the Doctor we're talking about.

19
00:01:02,320 --> 00:01:04,360
He's in a co-dependent relationship
with a screwdriver.

20
00:01:04,440 --> 00:01:07,600
I mean, if he had to choose between
an enormous complicated machine

21
00:01:07,680 --> 00:01:10,440
he could fix with a tool kit
and a girl, who would he go with?

22
00:01:11,600 --> 00:01:14,280
Yeah, you're right. Both of them.

23
00:01:14,360 --> 00:01:15,960
Using the same tool kit.

24
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:19,000
So what do we do?

25
00:01:21,320 --> 00:01:22,800
(SIGHS)

26
00:01:23,440 --> 00:01:26,360
I give in.
I'm going to go find my dumb bedroom.

27
00:01:26,440 --> 00:01:29,000
Do your worst.
Can't wait to see your next trick.

28
00:01:29,080 --> 00:01:30,080
Whoa!

29
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:32,240
Who the hell are you?

30
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:34,720
You, from tomorrow night.

31
00:01:37,960 --> 00:01:41,080
Okay. Where have you put it?

32
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:43,320
Where is my bedroom?

33
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:46,160
This isn't funny! I'm exhausted.
Where is it?

34
00:01:46,360 --> 00:01:48,120
You think you've got problems?

35
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,840
We've got to share a bed.

36
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:51,600
Oh, dear God.

37
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:54,080
(MULTIPLE CLARAS TALKING AT ONCE)

38
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:00,560
(ALL SHOUTING ANGRILY)

